<string_table>
    <string id="st_alarm_system">
        <text>Alarm System</text>
    </string>
    <string id="st_alarm_system_descr">
		<text>Field-made defense module assembled from Zone junk. Not pretty, not silent, but it buys precious seconds when the perimeter gets breached. \n \n
			%c[ui_white]PROPERTIES:\n
			%c[d_orange] • %c[ui_white] Placeable\n</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_artifact_harvester">
		<text>Artifact Harvester</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_artifact_harvester_descr">
		<text>A device to harvest different artifacts for resources. Artifacts loose condition while generating resources. \n \n
			%c[ui_white]PROPERTIES:\n
			%c[d_orange] • %c[ui_white] Placeable\n
			%c[d_orange] • %c[ui_white] Compatible artefacts: Anomalous Bread, Bubble, Crystal, Death Lamp, Fireball, Flame, Gravi, Meat Chunk, Pin, Snowflake, Sponge\n
			</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_pegboard">
		<text>Weapon pegboard</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_pegboard_descr">
		<text>A pegboard that can display up to three weapons. \n \n
			%c[ui_white]PROPERTIES:\n
			%c[d_orange] • %c[ui_white] Placeable\n</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_pegboard_pistol">
		<text>Pistol pegboard</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_pegboard_pistol_descr">
		<text>A pegboard that can display up to nine pistols. \n \n
			%c[ui_white]PROPERTIES:\n
			%c[d_orange] • %c[ui_white] Placeable\n</text>
	</string>
	<string id="st_headgear_display">
